{"tid":1299281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[請恢復二讀] 林鄭講「撤回」又有L用","createTime":"2019-07-09T04:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T05:51:59.000Z","uid":104803,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c3284e5f63a2c3a752b9e8cadae3cd5b773f9878","tid":1299281,"uid":104803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:30:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">一定有淺黃淺藍會覺得，條例死左就等於無事。<br />\n<br />\n依個時候你可以反問：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭講左就有法律效力？<br />\n答案係：無</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">咁既然無法律效力，咁大家做咩等著睇live呢？我也不知道，自己都係次次都有追live，口裡說不要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之，就算林鄭講左「撤回」，齋講嘅話都只係9up（何況而家係講壽終正寢）佢又唔係法律，要撤回既話，法夢講過程序係咁：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">跟返《議事規則》第64(2)條<br />\n<br />\n一、李家超係要致函立法會主席<br />\n二、預告恢復二讀<br />\n三、並在信中清楚講明恢復二讀目的係為左「撤回」<br />\n四、喺之後既立法會會議中，正式宣告「撤回《條例草案》」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">一旦政府採取了這一步，若然政府希望重新就此立法，就需要<span style=\"color: green;\">完全由頭重新展開立法程序。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">相關連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/625334667649883/posts/1126739770842701?s=100004714003899&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F625334667649883%2Fposts%2F1126739770842701%3Fs%3D100004714003899%26sfns%3Dmo&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1Ux5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=c690b5ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/625334667649883/posts/1126739770842701?s=100004714003899&amp;sfns=mo</a></span>"},{"pid":"6193e54e5b0b601b94682e45a673514530450992","tid":1299281,"uid":104803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:32:15.000Z","msg":"唔使浪費生命係林鄭身上了<br />\n佢當淺藍淺黃係on9<br />\n<br />\n我地好好諗文宣可以點講返清楚件事就得<br />\n大家一齊努力繼續抗爭啦～"},{"pid":"fa9c3c3a487378e541cf11001c8e913565089e6a","tid":1299281,"uid":104803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:33:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c45b9b40d8cd39c5d1346b7f101f8eb68847c55d","tid":1299281,"uid":104803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:58:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bff29d2f51732a1b46140a504127d5eb7dd00dd8","tid":1299281,"uid":236538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:58:57.000Z","msg":"絕不接受任何妥協<br />\n<br />\n政府已不能信任<br />\n<br />\n自由正被逐步侵蝕<br />\n<br />\n集中立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n持久戰我們必敗<br />\n<br />\n我要真&middot;雙普選！<br />\n<br />\n刻不容緩！！！"},{"pid":"a5d53ef92e038f255941306474d597bd5291c16f","tid":1299281,"uid":104803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:59:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ff7b662c9c48d6e996b3b5d367708a3764cc307","tid":1299281,"uid":7143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:59:26.000Z","msg":"唔好俾機會政府話我地拒絕對話，其實一路都同佢地對話緊<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dgptcT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dgptcT</a>"},{"pid":"de430cbc9be4bc51a98d13dc04d74d3d2ad66f9c","tid":1299281,"uid":104803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:01:22.000Z","msg":"趁lunch time狂推"},{"pid":"eb6c5ffaae9a650721b6af10b54ada247257af79","tid":1299281,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:03:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76ffcab02efad3199e14d1f0ae7810a8bbfa52f1","tid":1299281,"uid":104803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:04:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f16b95d4a8543b6909a584382caa91902251ecaa","tid":1299281,"uid":252684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jy2eRxp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjy2eRxp.png&h=c8f3abd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f840cb38277c295d1953dd7ced94e9e9c986e284","tid":1